# mogura analyze 示範:開票式漸進渲染 → 鑽入目錄 → 排序切換
Output demo/analyze.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Padding 12

Env MOGURA_LANG "en"

Type "mogura analyze ~/.cache"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 6s

Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Backspace
Sleep 1.5s

Type "s"
Sleep 1.5s
Type "s"
Sleep 1.5s
Type "s"
Sleep 1s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
